## Retrieve Company And It's Employees [/companies/{companyId}/employees]
This resource retrieves company and it's all employees identified by *company_id*.
This resource will return an object Company which has the following attributes.

+ companyId (number): the companyId
+ name (string) - name of the company
+ address (object) - an object which contains the adress of the company 
   + city (string):  Dubai
   + state (string): UAE
+ employee (array[string]) - array which contains all employees 
   + employeeId (number)
   + name  (string)
   + phoneNumber (string)
   + gender (enum[string]) - the gender can be MALE, FEMALE or OTHER 
   + dateOfBirth : (string)
   + salary (double)
   + company (number) - comapny's ID

+ Parameters
    + companyId: 1 (required, number) - ID of the company in form of an integer

### Retreive Company's And It's Employees [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
   
   + Body
       
              {
                    "companyId": 1,
                    "name": "Bayzat",
                    "address": {
                        "city": "Dubai",
                        "state": "UAE"
                    },
                    "employees": [{
                        "employeeId": 2,
                        "name": "John",
                        "phoneNumber": "+97111",
                        "gender": "MALE",
                        "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-14",
                        "salary": 1500.0,
                        "company": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "employeeId": 7,
